VALUES
  ('medical-tech-moex-05828', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-109-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', 'EML4（Echinoderm Microtubule Associated Protein Like 4）與ALK（Anaplastic lymphoma kinase）之融合基因 （EML4-ALK fusion gene）是肺腺癌中常見的一種染色體轉位（translocation）變異，下列何種方法最不適用 在檢測此種變異或其蛋白產物？', '["螢光原位雜交（FISH）", "RNA反轉錄後進行聚合酶連鎖反應（RT-PCR）", "免疫組織化學染色法（IHC）", "DNA桑格定序法（Sanger sequencing）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9d5fa0cfde76", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f3221475c56", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109020", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 75, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-05829', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-109-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '融合基因變異常見於血液腫瘤，而融合基因主要是由下列何種變異所產生？', '["點突變（point mutation）", "拷貝數變異（CNV）", "染色體轉位（translocation）", "外顯子（exon）框內刪除（in-frame deletion）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9d5fa0cfde76", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f3221475c56", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109020", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 76, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-05830', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-109-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '為避免分子檢驗室之污染，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["理想狀態需要至少3個空間，即pre-amplification room，amplification room及post-amplification room", "只要使用有棉塞過濾的tip，就可以在不同空間使用同一支微量吸管", "若空間不足，只要有適當區隔，試劑配製與檢體處理可合併在同一室", "人員進出不同空間的原則是採clean to dirty"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9d5fa0cfde76", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f3221475c56", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109020", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 77, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
